Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.02,0:01:54.03,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(620,360)}花\N井\N和\N美\N琴\N是\N青\N梅\N竹\N马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.02,0:01:54.03,zs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(28,310)}夏\N日\N的\N回\N忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.55,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 今天能游多远了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.61,0:02:04.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.25,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们两人完全没有进步嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:14.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经可以游20米了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.46,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5000米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.98,0:02:22.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么可以游这么远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴和今鸟是不是做了什么秘密特训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.74,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也让今鸟教我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.52,0:02:35.21,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 下次就由我来教天满吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.11,0:02:41.71,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 别得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不亏是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 今鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你擦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 天满 真体贴人啊 天满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.27,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫啊 热汤都洒到脚上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你擦的 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.42,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴你可真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.42,0:03:07.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他独处到这么晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.27,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做了些什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.27,0:03:11.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会一定要告诉我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.15,0:03:19.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴害羞了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.74,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨从刚才开始心情就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.17,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在嫉妒美琴和今鸟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.17,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 播磨喜欢的人是美琴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.72,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨 播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.98,0:03:39.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你出去说点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.73,0:03:40.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了…这么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.82,0:03:49.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天满终于发现我的魅力了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我已经听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.90,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨有个心上人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.74,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.23,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经告白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经暗示了好几次 可人家根本不理会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 她有时候是有点迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.29,0:04:12.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 现在正要开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.33,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨 好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨 是个好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.41,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话请和我交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感动啊 我可以拥抱你吗 天满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我练习告白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.91,0:04:43.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我喜…喜…喜…说不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.10,0:04:50.05,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 播磨 已经是23回了 认真点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.53,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你张这么壮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经{\pos(465,40)}幸福到极点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就由我来做个示范吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没露馅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.13,0:05:06.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.66,0:05:14.46,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很久之前 我就喜欢播磨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.42,0:05:23.10,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻度{\pos(170,40)}呼吸困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分 这么笑成这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想想我这是为了谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.74,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都已经示范了好几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多该领悟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.79,0:05:31.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我演得好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.46,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就换播磨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪里见过啊 在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么继续开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.68,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜… 说不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.55,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我再给你示范一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.62,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你也该领悟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是迟钝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.44,0:06:02.07,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个 虽然和刚才台词不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感觉很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有不好的回忆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.33,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉 错觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.61,0:06:19.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别管那件事 我们继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.07,0:06:20.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.43,0:06:32.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜…喜…喜… 说不出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.76,0:06:35.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面的感觉很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 我再示范一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么看都知道我喜欢你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能替我想想吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋是故意的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.44,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fsp3\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_中}塚{\r}本 就在那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.21,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡到她的旁边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良健太郎 弃权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.84,0:07:27.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D D 加油 D D 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D D 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.84,0:07:39.67,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D D 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.28,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(225,245)}到最后都没爬到正面的男子 今鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.47,0:07:45.35,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经转了5回了 差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了了 从后面也无所谓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.00,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(235,455)}今鸟 弃权 但是不能叫出声的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点就可以到天满旁边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,455)}从战场退避到安全圈的高野晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.53,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了 八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.29,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么处处和我过不去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.18,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 力气太大 要折了 要折了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.25,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我放手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.93,0:08:31.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:38.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.49,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗{\pos(170,455)}的时候把衣服脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.66,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨{\pos(310,440)} 弃权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.49,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没睡着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了个恶梦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶 待会给我看看摄像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.75,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要给你们看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.89,0:09:30.64,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.58,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春树 打的很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让空手道和别的流派进行比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这老爸也太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小春的确够格继承这家道场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.62,0:09:46.07,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是浪费了他的脑子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.07,0:09:47.19,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.05,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥三郎 你也夸奖一下自己的儿子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.05,0:09:50.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然轻而易举的把国家级选手给打倒了 周防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里 打得很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.65,0:10:02.92,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也赢了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹表现得高兴一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.83,0:10:06.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别站在这里装酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.93,0:10:07.73,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周防的生日宴会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然让我随意表演点什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.75,0:10:19.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可如果演砸了 周防又要生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.91,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出什么可以让大家高兴的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.81,0:10:29.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是男子汉春树怎么能让大家失望呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.27,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔术道具 什么都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么没有 有什么没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小学2年级的夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.71,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真弱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也能称上道场的儿子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.00,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这么弱了还练什么拳法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.65,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我自己也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.15,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是父亲强迫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.67,0:11:16.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书呆子只要老老实实地读书就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常被人欺负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.10,0:11:34.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.74,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春树 不可以剩饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去 会被美琴追上的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.36,0:11:49.76,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个比较适合动脑筋的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬拿我跟她比 我不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.79,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴生性开朗 是大家的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.19,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习完我们一起去吃凉面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都不能饿着自己哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.17,0:12:17.67,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没办法超过美琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.52,0:12:26.28,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 花井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.77,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都掉出来了 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是大家眼中的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.02,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是经常被欺负的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.49,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在很不相称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次上课时 要让大家在课堂上表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2个人一组哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.97,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.97,0:12:57.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可怕的“被全班所忽视”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己简直变成了空气一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不自然的感觉真让人吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.52,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 我就开始逃学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.32,0:13:18.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没做错什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:22.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的学校我才不想去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.80,0:13:28.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛子的表演啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.87,0:13:36.00,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是音乐课代表 所以老师让我两一组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.99,0:13:41.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去 我不去 绝对不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.83,0:13:46.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出来我就一直吹下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.02,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不需要却还是闹别扭的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.80,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既便如此 美琴还是每天都来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.28,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天最热的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.25,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刮大风的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.13,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下大雨的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.83,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴今天迟了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:14.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴 不是说今天不可以去学校的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跟我回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.40,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要待在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别任性了 你都已经感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.47,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.68,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于想通了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.04,0:14:32.05,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师催我们快点去表演呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.23,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴什么都没有说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.23,0:14:40.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感冒的事以及被妈妈阻止的事 还有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周防 你和男孩子组队 不害羞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺配的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.48,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候结婚设宴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.22,0:15:05.30,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们没有关系 一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.31,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么和花井组队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.31,0:15:12.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师不是让你和别人组队的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.32,0:15:18.03,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴不是因为老师才勉强和我组队的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.17,0:15:21.14,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和花井一组很丢人的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.22,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.84,0:15:30.22,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢人 有什么可丢人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.12,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我再看见你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.55,0:15:39.16,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 继续练习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.51,0:15:43.05,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴其实觉得很丢人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还走调了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我认真一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.41,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为像美琴一样的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.87,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花井 该你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 花井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.69,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云也一定要好好听啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.86,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看不到他心里的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:43.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个 花井春树 开始表演吹笛子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.71,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了啦 真差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.61,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美{\pos(605,400)}\N琴\N都\N忘\N的\N一\N干\N二\N净\N了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.26,0:18:48.93,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热 热 热死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云 空调怎么坏了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.09,0:18:55.09,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天姐姐扮演万石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.21,0:18:59.11,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋子里转 把空调给撞坏了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.23,0:19:03.53,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上电器店会来人修的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.53,0:19:07.65,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等不了等不了 我要化掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.38,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就用猜拳来决定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.06,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的一方可以去避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.53,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去有空调的地方玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输的留下来看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.45,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又擅自决定了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.90,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始 先出石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头 剪刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.09,0:19:31.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(605,250)}不\N要\N在\N家\N等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,350)}想\N出\N去\N玩 \N想\N出\N去\N玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,310)}出\N剪\N出\N剪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.02,0:19:31.78,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,300)}手\N势\NV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.94,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.37,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云玩这个可真弱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.81,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有看透对手的秘密绝招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样 偷看手的另外一侧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.84,0:19:46.96,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,290)}看\N不\N出\N的\N成\N分\N居\N多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.01,0:19:49.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.01,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.64,0:19:54.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电器店啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能来修理了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.36,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.36,0:20:11.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐回来之前 一定要想办法让家里凉快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.39,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.86,0:20:38.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让姐姐也来穿浴衣的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.49,0:20:42.26,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣 浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能把天热给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.70,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 打水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.39,0:21:17.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.41,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你洗洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.43,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.63,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么跑到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.57,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好凉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕 蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.65,0:21:56.95,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.99,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.59,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.65,0:22:09.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想要的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.24,0:22:14.60,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢 说给我听听吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.50,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在姐姐身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.34,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.34,0:22:21.32,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是八云的姐姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.33,0:22:41.84,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 那个…就用那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.26,0:22:44.31,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.31,0:22:46.24,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了冰激凌回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.11,0:22:51.56,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风铃啊 不错哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.83,0:22:55.55,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看着就能把天热给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.58,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好 八云
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.75,0:23:07.25,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fsp3\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_中}塚{\r}本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.41,0:23:10.23,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸 没想到能在这里碰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.98,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正准备去看角斗 一起去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.08,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.08,0:23:16.70,sub2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,40)}看过了吗 / 不可爱吗 / 请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.22,0:23:15.82,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 喧嚣学院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.02,0:23:18.89,sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乌丸一起去看角斗的约会啊
